About this item

  • The Latest Fully Upgraded Automatic Tent: With our latest designed pop-up tent, you will be an expert in camping and outdoor activities. The automatic hydraulic system of our camping tent allows you to set up or fold down the tent within 1 minute. The use of the most advanced carbon brazed support structure ensures that the tent can withstand severe weather storms. Say goodbye to the traditional rope tent!
  • Unique Three-layer Waterproof Tent: 68D 210T polyurethane-coated polyester PU 3000mm special waterproof coating material, three-layer structure, and exquisite waterproof and gluing process at each seam (zips, 4 corners, hooks, bottom) ensure that our latest automatic tent can withstand the summer storm weather. (Refer to the test results of the video please). The unique telescopic door design better ensures your perfect isolation from heavy rain.
  • Super-large Space and Extended Space Design: The well-designed 2 expandable porches (16.1 inches) increased the tent space by at least 30% to put camping gears. The upgraded large tent can accommodate at least 3 adults. Interior pockets and lantern hooks keep items clean and orderly. The backpack tent weighs only 4.24 kg (9.34 lb), 90.6 x 113 x 52 inches (outside), 82.7 x 70.9 x 43.3 inches (inside). Package size is only 31 x 7 x 7 inches.
  • Breathable and Stable: The unique double-door and mesh window design integrates ventilation and weatherproof functions. The upgraded elastic glass fiber rod with a diameter of 8.5 mm, the thickened and lengthened 10 ground steel stakes and 4 wind ropes ensure the tent has good wind resistance and stability. The high-quality double-SBS zippers has been tested for hundreds of times still remains smooth.
  • 2 in 1 Tent for Multifunction: Cflity 3-person tent is composed of a detachable outer tent and an inner tent. It as a whole can serve as a windproof and rainproof camping tent. The outer tent can be used as a sunshade, gazebo, awning, etc. Lets you enjoy sunbathing during the day and stargazing at night, giving you a romantic journey.

What's in the box?

  • 1 camping tent, 1 carry bag, 10 steel stakes, 4 ropes, 1 instruction manual

    • Product Description

    • Cflity lightweight tents are ideal for any avid hiker or camper looking to reduce weight on their backpack. It comes in weighing in at only 9.34lb, at approximately 90.6 in long and 113 in wide with the design of the extension door, the tent was constructed for 3 people.
    • Our tents are combined with lightweight and durable materials. Super fast and easy set up! Ideal for quick setup after long hikes. These key elements will ultimately provide you with more off-road experience.

    Expanding Space Design

    The dome tent has 2 extensible porches (each 16.1in)for all your equipment. And the unique extensible door ensures the inside dome tent is completely dry under any rainy situation. In heavy rain, rainwater will not enter the tent even if you leave the inner tent door open. The tent is roomy to accommodate 3 adults. 30% more space than similar tents.

    6th Gen. Hydraulic Spring Bracket

    The automatic hydraulic system of our camping tent allows you to set up or fold down the tent within 1 minute. All the poles are built in, just unfold and pop up.With a diameter of 8.5mm, our upgraded resilient fiberglass poles can withstand wind of up to 30mph, that will never break and have good wind resistance and stability.

    2 Featured D-shape Doors

    The unique double-door and mesh window design integrates ventilation and weatherproofing features. Both the inner and outer door are made of breathable polyester and can protect your privacy. The D-shape design of two doors allows both sides to be fully opened or closed, making it easy to get in and out and providing good visibility.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Amazon Customer
    5 out of 5 stars
    Bigger/heavier but totally worth it
    It’s definitely bigger and heavier than I expected. In the title it says “backpacking tent” but it’s folded-up footprint is quite large. I’ve managed to strap this beast to the outside of my rucksack. It’s very good quality so I’ll update this review once I use it on my homeless adventures over the next 2 months where it’ll definitely get some good use in all types of weather and scenarios. I never rate anything 5 stars (always room for improvement) so I’ll have to deduct a star for the fact that it’s stated in the title that it’s suitable for backpacking. Update coming soon. UPDATE: After using this tent in an urban environment for 2 months now…it’s a life saver. It’s the easiest setup/tear down tent I’ve ever had. You just kick the legs out and pull down the top handle and bam it’s all setup. It’s made of a sturdy material and doesn’t tear or rip easily. I’ve hit it with a hand saw by mistake and it didn’t even puncture. I’ve dragged it on branches and thorn bushes and it’s been fine. I haven’t used the tent stakes yet because I’m usually tucked back under a tree or in tight space. The fully erected footprint is relatively large, but I’ve never had an issue with it being too big. It’s definitely a three man tent but I’m using it solo so there’s plenty of room for activities…and storing gear. It’s survived many rainy nights. Water does pool on the roof, but that’s my fault for not putting up the rain fly or tightening it out. It does take up a bit more room in packed down form but I have a big ruck sack so it just sticks out the top of the bag. Overall, it’s probably the best tent I’ve had. The military should adopt a similar system. This tent isn’t far from military grade. Oh, the downside for me was the orange trim. I get the whole safety thing but I’ve spent time trying to cover the orange many times so I could remain hidden and out of view. Full green would be nice. Other than that, I totally recommend it.

      Key Features:

      Instant Pop-Up Design: The tent boasts an automatic hydraulic system that allows for quick and effortless setup in under a minute. Simply unfold the tent, and it will automatically pop up into its desired shape.
      Three-Layer Waterproof Construction: The tent features a unique three-layer design, consisting of a high-quality polyester outer tent, a waterproof inner tent, and a durable floor. This construction ensures excellent protection against rain, wind, and other elements, keeping you dry and comfortable throughout your camping adventures.
      Spacious Interior: With ample interior space measuring 80.7 x 70.9 x 45.3 inches (internal) and 88.6 x 78.7 x 53.1 inches (external), the tent comfortably accommodates three adults. The large double doors and well-ventilated mesh windows provide easy access and ample airflow, ensuring a pleasant stay.
      Extensible Porches: The tent comes with two extensible porches that can be used for additional storage space, creating a versatile area for your gear and equipment.
      Portable and Lightweight: The tent folds down into a compact size of 31 x 7 x 7 inches and weighs only 10.47 pounds, making it easy to transport and carry on your camping trips.
      Durable and Wind-Resistant: The tent is constructed with sturdy fiberglass poles that can withstand winds up to 30 mph, ensuring stability and peace of mind in various weather conditions.
      Benefits:

      Easy and Fast Setup: The instant pop-up design eliminates the hassle of traditional tent assembly, saving you valuable time and energy.
      Superior Waterproofing: The three-layer construction provides exceptional protection against rain and moisture, ensuring a dry and comfortable sleeping experience, even in inclement weather.
      Ample Space: The spacious interior offers plenty of room for three adults to relax and move around comfortably, with additional storage space provided by the extensible porches.
      Versatile Design: The versatile design allows you to use the outer tent as a sunshade, gazebo, or awning, expanding its functionality and adaptability.
      Portability and Lightweight: The compact size and lightweight design make the tent easy to transport and carry, making it a convenient option for backpacking and hiking trips.
      Potential Drawbacks:

      Limited Ventilation: While the mesh windows provide some ventilation, some users may find the tent to be somewhat warm in hot weather.
      Condensation: The three-layer construction may contribute to some condensation buildup on the inner tent, especially in humid conditions.
      Price: Compared to some other similar tents, the Cflity 3 Man Instant Pop Up Tent may be slightly more expensive.
      Overall:

      The Cflity 3 Man Instant Pop-Up Tent is an excellent choice for campers seeking a reliable, easy-to-use, and weatherproof option. Its instant setup, spacious interior, and durable construction make it a versatile and convenient option for a wide range of camping scenarios. While it may have some minor drawbacks, such as limited ventilation and potential condensation, these are generally manageable trade-offs for the overall benefits offered by this tent.
